 </p>
 <p>
   <b>(3) Paragraph:</b> 4.3.1
 </p>
 <p>
   <b>(5) Comment:</b>
 </p>
 <p>
Entity address_based_location_representation. It is not understandable why the postale-address is of type address_assignment which requires a person or organization. There are cases when we simply want to specify a house or real_estate only by its address not knowing about a specific person or organization at this address; e.g. for maintenance of the water meter in a multi flat house.</p>
